[330956.266548] Hardware name: Dell Inc. PowerEdge R630/02C2CP, BIOS 2.6.0 10/26/2017
[330956.274996] Call Trace:
[330956.277828]  [&amp;lt;ffffffff9b781400&amp;gt;] dump_stack+0x19/0x1b
